## Extended AMAN (Arrival Manager)

**Purpose**: Extended arrival sequencing for major airports

**Specification**: EUROCAE ED-254

**Requirements**:
- **EAMAN-004**: Service provision as per ED-254
- **EAMAN-006**: Upstream ATSU consumption compliance

**Service Bindings**:
- **WS-Light**: Arrival Sequence Publisher interface (REQ-017254)
- **AMQP Messaging**: Arrival Sequence Subscriber interface (REQ-0200)

**Payload Schemas**: Defined in Service Description Document

**EASA Regulation**: DS.GE (2013/1768) for Extended AMAN equipment

**Note**: Multiple deployment milestones with specific requirements

